sentences: Kim Jin-tae (Hangul: 김진태; born December 19, 1980), better known by his stage name Verbal Jint (Hangul: 버벌진트), is a South Korean rapper, record producer and musician who is known for his groundbreaking innovations in Korean hip hop rhyme schemes.
Before Verbal Jint's official debut in 2001, Korean hip hop lacked a fundamental component of rap, the rhyming.
